<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(عس)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> قوله تعالى:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> <span class="c3">{مِنْ شَرِّ الْوَسْااسِ الْخَنّاسِ}</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>هو إبليس لعنه الله، وقد تقدّم ذكره، والحمد لله.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
